一線服務提供者應該具備那些條件？（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:37:08+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "67b2583cbd87", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112150", "c": "503", "s": "0909", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "社會福利服務", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試外交領事人員及外交行政人員考試、國際經濟商務人員考試、民航人員考試、原住民族考試", "original_question_number": "三", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "aboriginal", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('aboriginal-64311456-moex-00144', 'aboriginal-64311456', 'aboriginal-64311456-moex-112-d44949ff', 'sub-aboriginal-64311456-08', NULL, 'essay', '社會福利服務提供的方式包括現金給付、實物給付或服務給付，各具其
